[DNA fingerprinting (restriction endonuclease analysis) comparing the human and caprine strains of the enterohemorrhagic _E. coli_ would definitively prove the relationship or not. Sheep and goats in petting zoos or elsewhere can be reservoirs for human EHEC infection. - Mod.LL

